      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHIFTY BREEZE (2) stuck on well last time to finish one length back in third (20.03) at this track in a Mix 5 over 366m. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and two minor placings from four starts. Racing well and deserves a win. DOUGLAS (4) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 19.93 beating Christmas Day. The form from his last run stacks up well. Form should stack up. NANA MARIE (7) had been racing in honest fashion recording three placings in a row before finishing fourth (20.16) at this track latest. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Should play a prominent role. JET SPRINGER (8) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
